      <b data-is-speakable>Lessons Learned From New York's Fix For Surprise Medical Bills : Shots - Health News</b>   <b data-is-speakable>As Congress considers legislation to end surprise medical billing, some are looking at lessons learned from New York's experiment with "baseball-style" arbitration.</b>
